About QLove

QLove is the flagship brand of Q Korea Co., Ltd., established in 2014. We specialize in natural mineral hair coloring and advanced scalp & hair health solutions, operating across 4,000+ partner locations.

Our mission is to deliver safe and effective beauty services:

  • Ammonia-free mineral-based hair coloring
  • Professional scalp & hair treatments suitable for all customers, including pregnant individuals and those with sensitivities
  • Functional wellness supplements to support overall health

Driven by innovation and care, QLove continues to expand its wellness network worldwide, ensuring every customer enjoys vibrant, healthy hair and holistic well-being.
